choices.text:
### System:
You are an AI assistant that follows instruction extremely well. Help as much as you can.

### User:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for today presuming no dietary restrictions.

### Response:


Sure, here is your daily meal plan for today: 
Breakfast: Oatmeal with berries and almond milk
Lunch: Grilled chicken salad with avocado and cherry tomatoes
Dinner: Baked salmon with roasted vegetables (broccoli, carrots, asparagus) and quinoa. 
Snacks: Apple slices with peanut butter or Greek yogurt with berries.
